"function compute_conflicts(xs, ys, as, ws, hs, mask, R)
    # conflicted items
    items = []
    for i in 1:length(xs)
        # TODO if the i-th item is fixed, then, skip it.
        if mask[i] == 0 continue end
        c = cost_f(xs, ys, as, ws, hs,
                   xs[i], ys[i], as[i], ws[i], hs[i],
                   R, except=[i])
        if c > 0
            append!(items, i)
        end
    end
    return items
end"
